| Sample-1             | ds.3bcc5de2a1874faebbb0c15171a9c5e2 | AdliLab      | illumina.fastq.v1.8 |
### see how to download
bs download --help
### download dataset with the dataset id
bs download dataset --id ds.cd52576212ea4786bf1a04aa0a67b8e4 -o /data/adli/adlilab/Runs/20200115_Alex/
